name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
The CIA has changed its official position on the origin of the new coronavirus, saying on Saturday that the new coronavirus is more likely to have originated in a laboratory than to have been transmitted through animals.
With this conclusion, the CIA has joined the FBI and the Department of Energy in believing that the virus is more likely to have originated from a laboratory accident.
The CIA director told the media: "We will no longer sit idly by," and he believes that the new coronavirus was leaked from the Wuhan Institute of Virology.
A CIA spokesman said in a statement on Saturday: "The CIA has assessed with a "lower confidence" conclusion that a natural origin is less likely than a laboratory origin related to the research on the new coronavirus."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, Anhui Satellite TV invited a deaf-mute delivery boy to the Spring Festival Gala. However, netizens found that the delivery boy had a greasy face. His Douyin account also posted luxury cars, watches, and fitness routines. He was suspected of identity fraud, which caused heated discussions. Anhui Satellite TV stated: The work record is complete and can be checked. The delivery boy registered in October 2019. As of now, he has joined the food delivery platform for 1,938 days and has completed 62,642 orders in total. Among them, a total of 11,259 orders were delivered from August to December 24.
